		ONE OF THE GREATEST STARTS TO A WORLD CUP IN HISTORY!#WorldCup⁠ ⁠#GER⁠ ⁠#MEX⁠ ⁠#GERMEX pic.twitter.com/cRM6Ayz9Dj But despite almost constant pressure, they were largely kept at long range and their poor finishing rarely threatened Ochoa as Mexico held out for only their second victory against the Germans in 12 attempts. Reuters